                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870912-58-victim607 t17870912-58-viclabel277"></join>; I lost two china figures, on the 24th of July; I was not present at the time; they were found on the prisoner in Christ's Hospital.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17870912-58-person609">
                  ISAAC
